<!--
  Frozen PubMed efetch response used to regression-test the
  similar_cases_search skill. Two PMIDs are seeded:

  - 99999001: a fully-populated record. The expected BibTeX entry has every
    optional field (volume, number, doi).
  - 99999002: a sparse record. The expected BibTeX entry must OMIT doi and
    number rather than insert a placeholder. This guards against the most
    common failure mode (hallucinating missing metadata).

  PMIDs in the 9999900x range are fictitious to avoid colliding with real
  PubMed records during any accidental network call.
-->
